name: 透
text:
なんか言って
言ってほしい、プロデューサー
trans:
Tell me something.
Anything. I want you to, Producer.

text:
ひとりじゃないぞ
俺も一緒だ
trans:
You're not alone.
I'll be right there
with you.

text:
信じてくれ
透のこと

name: 透
text:
……ふふっ
やばい、刺さる、それ
trans:
...fufu.
Oh no. My heart. That went straight through.

name: プロデューサー
text: （よかった。安心してくれたかな）
trans: (Phew. She seems like she got a little peace of mind.)

name: 透
text:
……うん
それしかないよね
trans:
...yeah.
Nothing else but that, is there.

name: 透
text:
ふふっ
セリフっぽいよ
trans:
Fufu.
That's a straight-up line, c'mon.

name: プロデューサー
trans: (Did that not get across to her, maybe...?)
